            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 text-center">Tell me your purpose for contacting Mishelle, and I'll help you draft a message based on her profile.</p>
            <div class="mb-4">
                <label for="purposeInput" class="block text-gray-700 text-sm font-bold mb-2">Your Purpose:</label>
                <textarea id="purposeInput" rows="3" class="shadow appearance-none border rounded-lg w-full py-3 px-4 text-gray-700 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500" placeholder="e.g., 'I'm a recruiter interested in your PR experience' or 'I'd like to collaborate on an event.'"></textarea>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center mb-6">
                <button id="generateMessageBtn" class="btn-primary text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-full focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline flex items-center justify-center mx-auto">
                    <span id="buttonText">Generate Message</span>
                    <svg id="loadingSpinner" class="animate-spin -ml-1 mr-3 h-5 w-5 text-white hidden" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
